data.description: Welcome to the gated community of Larimar! Enjoy the beautiful views and sunsets of Lake Erie from your deck, master bedroom or lower patio! The lake can be seen from living room and dining room also, with walk-out deck. The kitchen and breakfast bar have an open concept, awesome for entertaining. There are granite countertops throughout the house, with stainless steel appliances, washer/dryer, centralized vacuum system and Alexa-enabled smart home, all included with the home! The first floor has hardwood flooring throughout, with carpeted bedrooms and stairs. The high vaulted ceilings and large windows capture all the natural daylight. Lower-level walkout is designed for your viewing pleasure of the lake. Upstairs, you will find the primary suite with a full bath including soaking tub, separate shower and large walk-in closet with Amish-built custom shelves. There are 2 more bedrooms with spacious closets and another full bath on the second level. The fully finished walk-out lower level has a family room or bonus room with a half bath and storage area. Private beach access with a fire pit area for homeowners at the end of the street. The community is gated, private, and across from a large shopping area with multiple grocery stores and even a Starbucks! 20 minutes from downtown and 5 mins from highway system and Willowick Park. Seller offering buyer credit at closing.
